data.description: This move-in-ready 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den in Skyline Acres is ready to welcome you with open arms. You’ll appreciate its central location, which provides easy access to nearby schools, shopping centers, and major highways. Say goodbye to long commutes and hello to a more convenient lifestyle! Upon arrival, you'll immediately notice the fresh paint job that has been meticulously done both inside and out. The exterior showcases a modern metal roof, providing durability and a sleek aesthetic. The covered carport offers protection for your vehicles, while the screened-in porch invites you to relax and enjoy the beautiful weather year-round. One of the standout features of this property is the spacious backyard, complete with a shed that boasts working electrical outlets and is perfect for a workshop or additional storage. Also, there's plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or entertaining guests. The new vinyl fence surrounding the property ensures privacy. Prepare to be wowed by the newly remodeled kitchen, featuring brand-new cabinets and countertops that exude elegance and provide plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. The new ceiling fans throughout the home help keep the space cool and comfortable, even during warm summer days. Revel in the sleek and low-maintenance new vinyl flooring that stretches throughout the property, creating a seamless and cohesive look. As an added bonus, the built-in Bluetooth speakers in the ceiling allow you to effortlessly stream your favorite music and create the perfect ambiance for any occasion. Rest easy knowing that this property is equipped with a security system. When it's time to unwind, retreat to the cozy bedrooms, each offering a tranquil space to relax and recharge. With three bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or a dedicated home office. Come and see this exceptional property in Skyline Acres.
